{
  "Electromagnetic Induction": "电磁诱导",
  "This lesson covers the fundamental measures of center used to analyze and summarize data sets. You'll learn how to calculate and apply the mean, median, and mode, and understand when each is most appropriate.": "这个课程涵盖了分析和总结数据集的中心的基本测量方法。 您将学会如何计算和应用平均值、 中位数和模式, 并了解何时最合适 。",
  "A coil with 200 turns experiences a flux change of 0.05 Wb in 0.1 s. What is the induced EMF?": "有200转的卷圈经历0.1秒中0.05 Wb的通量变化。 诱导的EMF是什么?",
  "EMF = N * delta_Phi/delta_t = 200 * 0.05/0.1 = 100 V.": "EMF = N * delta_Phi/delta_t = 200 * 0.05/0.1 = 100 V。",
  "What is 'electromagnetic induction'?": "什么是电磁感应?",
  "Electromagnetic induction is the generation of an EMF when the magnetic flux through a circuit changes, discovered by Faraday and Henry.": "电磁感应是法拉第和亨利发现电路变化后磁通量产生的EMF。",
  "What is 'Faraday's law of induction'?": "什么是“星期五的诱导法则”?",
  "Faraday's law: EMF = -N*d(Phi)/dt. The minus sign (Lenz's law) indicates the induced EMF opposes the flux change.": "法拉第法:EMF = - N*d(菲)/dt。减号(列兹法)表示诱发的EMF反对通量变化。",
  "What is an 'eddy current'?": "什么是“潮流”?",
  "Eddy currents are loops of current induced in conductors by changing B fields. They cause heating and are used in induction cooktops and braking systems.": "艾迪海流是导体通过改变 B 字段而导引的电流循环,它们导致供暖,并用于上岗烹饪和制动系统。",
  "What is 'self-inductance'?": "什么是\"自我引导\"?",
  "Self-inductance L measures a coil's tendency to oppose changes in its own current. The induced back-EMF is EMF = -L*dI/dt.": "自我引导L 量测了卷圈反对其当前变化的倾向。 诱导回流EMF是 EMF = - L*dI/dt 。",
  "What is 'back-EMF'?": "什么是\"后援EMF\"?",
  "Back-EMF is the voltage induced in an inductor that opposes the current change. In motors, it opposes the applied voltage.": "后电磁场是导电器中引发的电压,它反对当前的变化。在发动机中,它反对应用的电压。",
  "What is 'motional EMF'?": "什么是情感EMF?",
  "Motional EMF = BvL is generated when a conductor of length L moves at speed v perpendicular to field B.": "当L长度的导体以速度移动或垂直移动到字段B时,即产生运动式EMF = BvL。",
  "A power station generator has a coil of 500 turns, each with area 0.1 m2, rotating at 60 Hz in a 0.8 T field. What is the peak EMF?": "发电站发电机有500个转圈,每个转圈的面积为0.1平方米,在0.8T田60赫兹旋转。电磁放大系数峰值是多少?",
  "EMF_peak = NAB*omega = 500*0.1*0.8*(2*pi*60) = 40*120*pi = 4800*pi = 15,080 V.": "EMF_peak = NAB*omega = 500*0.1*0.8* (2*pi*60) = 40*120*pi = 4800*pi = 15 080 V。",
  "A guitar pickup uses electromagnetic induction: a vibrating steel string changes the flux through a coil. If the flux varies as Phi = 10^-6 * sin(2*pi*440*t) Wb and the coil has 5000 turns, what is the peak EMF?": "吉他皮卡使用电磁感应:振动钢弦通过卷圈改变通量。如果通量以菲=10-6*sin(2*pi*440*t)Wb和卷圈有5000转,那么电磁放大系数的峰值是多少?",
  "EMF_peak = N*Phi_max*omega = 5000*1e-6*2*pi*440 = 5e-3*2764 = 13.8 V... Let me recalculate: 5000*1e-6 = 5e-3. omega = 2*pi*440 = 2764. EMF = 5e-3*2764 = 13.8 V. That seems too high. Actually 5000*10^-6 = 0.005 Wb. 0.005*2764 = 13.8 V. But for a guitar pickup that's too high. The flux should be much smaller. Let me adjust: EMF_peak = N*Phi_0*omega = 5000*1e-6*2764 = 13.8 mV assuming Phi_0 = 10^-9. Actually with Phi = 10^-6 as given, 5000*10^-6*2764 = 0.005*2764 = 13.82 V. Hmm, the question says 10^-6 so peak EMF = about 13.8 V. Let me change the flux to match mV range.": "EMF=2*pi*440=5e-3*2764=13.8 V...让我重新计算:5000*1e-6=5e-3.omga=2*pi*440=2764。EMF=5e-3*2764=13.8 V.这似乎太高。实际上,5000*10-6=0.005 Wb.0.005*2764=13.8V.但吉他皮卡太高,通量应小得多。让我调整:EMF_peak=N*Phi_0*0*omga=50001e-62764=13.8V,假设Phi_0=10=10*-32764=0.005 Wb.005*2764=0.005*2764=13.8V.hmm.问题如此高峰 EMF=6=13.8 V.请将我改变通量范围至13.8V.",
  "A wind turbine generator has blades that turn at 15 rpm. The generator coil has 200 turns, area 0.5 m2, in a 1.2 T field. What is the peak EMF?": "风力涡轮机发电机的叶片在每分钟15分钟时旋转。发电机圆圈有200转,面积为0.5平方米,在1.2 T 字段中。电磁放大系数峰值是多少?",
  "omega = 15*(2*pi/60) = pi/2 rad/s. EMF_peak = NAB*omega = 200*0.5*1.2*(pi/2) = 120*(pi/2) = 60*pi = 188.5 V.": "奥米加=15*(2*pi/60)=pi/2 rad/s. EMF_peak=NAB*omega=200*0.5*1.2*(pi/2)=120*(pi/2)=60*pi=188.5 V.",
  "A search coil with 100 turns and area 5 cm2 is flipped 180 degrees in a 0.2 T field in 0.05 s. What average EMF is induced?": "在0.05 s 的0.2 T 字段中,一个有100个旋转圈的搜索圈和面积为 5 cm2, 翻转180 度。",
  "Delta_Phi per turn = 2*B*A = 2*0.2*5e-4 = 2e-4 Wb (flux reverses). EMF = N*Delta_Phi/Delta_t = 100*2e-4/0.05 = 0.4 V.": "Delta_Phi 每转转2*B*A=2*0.2*5e-4=2e-4 Wb(逆流),EMF=N*Delta_Phi/Delta_t=100*2e-4/0.05=0.4V。",
  "A transformer has 1000 primary turns and 100 secondary turns. If the input is 120 V AC, the output voltage is:": "变压器有1000个初级转弯和100个二级转弯。如果输入为120 VAC,输出电压为:",
  "V_s/V_p = N_s/N_p. V_s = 120*(100/1000) = 12 V. This is a step-down transformer.": "V_s/V_p = N_s/N_p.V_s = 120*(100/1000) = 12V. 这是一个自下而上的变压器 。",
  "A regenerative braking system in an electric car converts kinetic energy to electrical energy. If the car decelerates from 20 m/s to 0 in 10 s and the generator produces an average of 5000 W, how much energy is recovered?": "电动汽车的再生制动系统将动能转换成电能,如果汽车减速从20米/秒减速到10秒零秒,发电机平均产生5000瓦,则回收多少能量?",
  "Energy = P*t = 5000*10 = 50,000 J = 50 kJ.": "能源 = P*t = 5000 *10 = 50 000 J = 50 kJ。"
}